J2aDVlrDTfs.title: Women`s Month Challenge: Car Tyre Change
J2aDVlrDTfs.description:
After my birthday month(April) and of course December, August is my fave month because its women`s month.Its normally filled with affirmations, sisterly love and celebration of all things women .Last year in order to celebrate this month I bought myself flowers every week during August,this year I decided to take it up a notch and challenged myself by learning how to change a car tyre. Yes I know, nothing girly about it but I must admit it was a lot easier and more fun than I anticipated.

 My Volkswagen (Botswana) family helped me out with this one.
(And  to keep all your car tyres & accessories in check or in times of emergency, the ‘Wescare’ from Wesbank (Botswana) offers great assistance.)

Happy women`s month ladies and do challenge yourself to do a lil something different as you celebrate just how phenomenal you are this month ;)
